1970;;The Mind of Mr. Soames;;British;;Alan Cooke;;Terence Stamp, Robert Vaughn;;sci-fi;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Mind_of_Mr._Soames;;The film tells the story of a thirty-year-old man (John Soames) who has been in a coma since a brain injury during birth. Now revived, he shows the behavior of a child and is monitored by two doctors attempting to find out if he can be rehabilitated in the adult world.